These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: spinach, eggplant, lemon
The people have 3 different jobs:  dancer, teacher, accountant
1. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4
2. the dancer is on the left or right of the accountant##3
3. the dancer is the person eating eggplant##1
4. the person eating lemon is on the far left##1
5. the teacher is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | lemon | spinach | eggplant |
| Job    | teacher    | accountant | dancer |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, collecting, sudoku
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, skateboard, jet-ski
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | collecting | sudoku | woodworking |
| Transport   | jet-ski    | skateboard     | bus        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: camping, reading, video-games
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: techno, disco, jazz
1. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the fan of techno##1
2. the fan of disco is on the left of the fan of techno##1
3. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | video-games     | reading | camping |
| Music-Genre   | disco | techno     | jazz  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, drama, epic
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, soccer, cycling
1. the person watching drama movies is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person watching animation movies is the person who's sport is cycling##1
3. the person watching drama movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | epic | drama  | animation  |
| Sport         | sailing  | soccer | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, singing, skydiving
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, indian, german
1. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is writing and the turkish##2
2. the person who's hobby is singing is in an odd position##4
3. the german is on the left of the turkish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | writing   | skydiving | singing    |
| Nationality   | indian | german     | turkish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: magic-tricks, rock-climbing, singing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, cycling, biathlon
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is cycling##1
2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | rock-climbing | singing | magic-tricks   |
| Sport   | biathlon     | rugby    | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: scientific, time-travel, animation
3 different pets are kept: mouse, hedgehog, snake
1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is between the owner of the snake and the person watching animation movies##2
3. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the owner of the mouse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | scientific | time-travel |
| Pet           | hedgehog         | mouse         | snake |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, mango, asparagus
3 different pets are kept: cat, hamster, horse
1. the owner of the cat is between the owner of the hamster and the person eating broccoli##2
2. the owner of the horse is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | mango | asparagus | broccoli |
| Pet    | hamster    | cat | horse     |

