.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, blues, techno
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: golf, cricket, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
3. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left of the fan of blues##1
4. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | techno   | blues  | electronic  |
| Sport         | rowing | cricket | golf |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: water, almond-milk, soy-milk
There 3 different types of food: lemon, asparagus, potato
1. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person eating potato is in an even position##4
3. the person eating potato is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | water    | soy-milk      | almond-milk |
| Food       | asparagus | potato | lemon   |

