.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-11::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  videographer, chef, analyst
The people use 3 different means of transport: van, motorbike, tram
1. the analyst is on the right of the chef##1
2. the person driving the van is the videographer##1
3. the person driving the tram is the analyst##1
4. the analyst is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | chef | analyst | videographer |
| Transport   | motorbike | tram   | van |

