.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: russian, spanish, brazilian
The people use 3 different means of transport: snowmobile, subway, bus
1. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
2. the russian is the person driving the bus##1
3. the person driving the subway is on the left or right of the spanish##3
4. the person driving the bus is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |     3      |
| Nationality   | brazilian | spanish | russian |
| Transport     | subway     | snowmobile   | bus        |

