.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-13::.
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, nigerian, russian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, skiing, snowboarding
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the russian##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the nigerian##1
3. the russian is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |
| Nationality   | russian  | brazilian | nigerian   |
| Sport         | skiing | snowboarding   | skateboarding |

