.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, traveling, camping
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, ferret, frog
1. the person who's hobby is camping is between the person who's hobby is traveling and the owner of the ferret##2
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | traveling | camping | drawing |
| Pet     | hedgehog    | frog  | ferret   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: animation, thriller, adventure
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: r&b, d&b, salsa
1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
2. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
3. the fan of d&b is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3
4. the person watching adventure movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation  | adventure     | thriller |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | r&b | salsa    |

