.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-18::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: fishing, filmmaking, writing
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: electronic, metal, blues
1. the fan of blues is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is writing is the fan of metal##1
4. the fan of electronic is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | writing | fishing   | filmmaking |
| Music-Genre   | metal   | electronic | blues      |

