.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-20::.
3 different pets are kept: frog, chinchilla, snake
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, soccer, cricket
1. the person who's sport is cricket is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the owner of the snake is in an even position##4
4. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |
| Pet     | chinchilla  | snake   | frog |
| Sport   | cricket | soccer | skateboarding       |

 